#: plugins/current_loop_tanks_monitor/templates/current_loop_tanks_monitor_setup.html:346
msgid ""
"As long as the level does not rise above this level, it will not allow "
"sending an email when the level drops to the minimum. This is used to block "
"the constant sending of emails when the level is at a minimum."
msgstr ""
"Dokud hladina nestoupne nad tuto úroveň, nedovolí odeslání e-mailu, když "
"úroveň klesne na minimum. Slouží k blokování neustálého odesílání e-mailů, "
"když je úroveň na minimu."

