msgstr "Stanice modbus - nápověda"

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:8
msgid "Modbus RTU Relay"
msgstr "Relé Modbus RTU"

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:9
msgid ""
"The industrial module controlled via the RS485 bus uses the Modbus RTU "
"protocol."
msgstr ""
"Průmyslový modul ovládaný po sběrnici RS485 využívá protokol Modbus RTU."

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:10
#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:71
msgid "Buy example on"
msgstr "Koupit například na"

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:12
msgid ""
"The durable case made of high-quality ABS plastic enables easy mounting on "
"the DIN bar."
msgstr ""
"Odolné pouzdro z vysoce kvalitního PLASTU ABS umožňuje snadnou montáž na DIN "
"lištu."

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:17
msgid ""
"Thanks to the configurable device address (1~255) on the RS485 bus, multiple "
"devices can be cascaded. If many devices are cascaded or the communication "
"distance is too long, RS485 repeaters should be used."
msgstr ""
"Díky konfigurovatelné adrese zařízení (1 ~ 255) na sběrnici RS485 lze "
"kaskádovat více zařízení. Pokud je mnoho zařízení kaskádovitě rozloženo nebo "
"je komunikační vzdálenost příliš dlouhá, je třeba použít opakovače RS485."

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:19
msgid ""
"Relay connection diagram. Rated current of the built-in relay contacts: up "
"to 10A 250V AC nebo 30 V DC. Direct control of household appliances: 230 V "
"AC or devices below 30 V DC."
msgstr ""
"Schéma připojení relé. Jmenovitý proud vestavěných kontaktů relé: do 10A "
"250V AC nebo 30 V DC. Přímé ovládání domácích spotřebičů: 230 V AC nebo "
"zařízení pod 30 V DC."

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:21
msgid ""
"Built-in Optocoupler isolation prevents interference from an external high-"
"voltage circuit connected to the relay."
msgstr ""
"Vestavěná izolace - optočlen zabraňuje zpětnému rušení z externího "
"vysokonapěťového obvodu připojeného k relé."

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:22
msgid ""
"Anti-reverse circuit prevents accidental damage to the circuit by incorrect "
"connection."
msgstr ""
"Obvod proti zpětnému chodu zabraňuje náhodnému poškození obvodu nesprávným "
"připojením."

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:23
msgid "High quality relay, contact rating: ≤10A 250V AC/30V DC."
msgstr ""
"Vysoce kvalitní relé, jmenovité hodnoty kontaktů: ≤10A 250V AC / 30V DC."

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:24
msgid "ABS plastic cover for rail mounting, easy to install, safe to use."
msgstr ""
"ABS plastový kryt pro montáž na lištu, snadná instalace, bezpečné použití."

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:25
msgid "3 LEDs for indicating MCU status and signal transmission status."
msgstr "3 LED diody pro indikaci stavu MCU a stavu přenosu signálu."

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:26
msgid "Supply voltage: 5 V."
msgstr "Napájecí napětí: 5 V."

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:27
msgid "Communication interface: RS485."
msgstr "Komunikační rozhraní: RS485."

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:28
msgid "Baud rate: 4800, 9600, 19200, 38400, 57600, 115200, 128000, 256000."
msgstr ""
"Přenosová rychlost: 4800, 9600, 19200, 38400, 57600, 115200, 128000, 256000."

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:29
msgid "Default communication format: 9600, N, 8, 1."
msgstr "Výchozí komunikační formát: 9600, N, 8, 1."

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:30
msgid "Form of contacts: 1NO 1NC."
msgstr "Typ kontaktů: 1NO 1NC."

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:31
msgid "Communication protocol: Standard Modbus RTU protocol."
msgstr "Komunikační protokol: Standardní protokol Modbus RTU."

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:32
msgid "RS485 address: 1-255."
msgstr "RS485 adresa: 1-255."

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:33
msgid "Number of relay channels: 8."
msgstr "Počet reléových kanálů: 8."

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:34
msgid ""
"RS485 terminal protection: 600 W lightning arrester and surge protection, 15 "
"KV ESD protection (dedicated solder pads with 120 R compensation resistor)."
msgstr ""
"Ochrana svorek RS485: 600 W bleskojistka a přepěťová ochrana, 15 KV ESD "
"ochrana (vyhrazené pájecí podložky s kompenzačním odporem 120 R)."

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:35
msgid "LED indicators"
msgstr "LED indikace"

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:36
msgid "STA"
msgstr "STA"

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:37
msgid "MCU indicator, flashes when the MCU is working normally."
msgstr "Indikátor MCU bliká, když MCU pracuje normálně."

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:38
msgid "TXD"
msgstr "TXD"

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:39
msgid "TX indicator, lights up when sending data."
msgstr "Tx indikátor, rozsvítí se při odesílání dat."

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:40
msgid "RXD"
msgstr "RXD"

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:41
msgid "RX indicator, lights up when receiving data."
msgstr "Indikátor RX, se rozsvítí při příjmu dat."

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:43
msgid "Command format"
msgstr "Formát příkazu"

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:44
msgid "The command contains 8 bytes."
msgstr "Příkaz obsahuje 8 bajtů."

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:45
msgid "Byte 1：Device Address"
msgstr "Bajt 1: Adresa zařízení"

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:46
msgid "Byte 2：Function code"
msgstr "Bajt 2: Kód funkce"

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:47
msgid "Byte 3 4：Address of register (big-endian)"
msgstr "Byte 3 4: Adresa registru (big-endian)"

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:48
msgid "Byte 5 6：data of register (big-endian)"
msgstr "Byte 5 6: Data registru (big-endian)"

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:49
msgid "Byte 7 8：CRC16 cheksum (little-endian)"
msgstr "Byte 7 8: CRC16 kontrolní součet (little-endian)"

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:50
msgid "Function code"
msgstr "Kód funkce"

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:51
msgid "01 Read state of Relay"
msgstr "01 Čtení stavu relé"

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:52
msgid "03 Read address, revision"
msgstr "03 Čtení adresy, verze FW"

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:53
msgid "05 Write single Relay"
msgstr "05 zapsat do jednoho relé"

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:54
msgid "06 Configure baudrate, address"
msgstr "06 Nastavení přenosové rychlosti, adresa"

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:55
msgid "0F Write all Relays"
msgstr "0F zapsat do všech relé"

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:56
msgid ""
"Examples： [Device with address 01]: Open Relay 0: 01 05 00 00 FF 00 8C 3A"
msgstr ""
"Příklad: [Zařízení s adresou 01]: vypnuté relé 0: 01 05 00 00 FF 00 8C 3A"

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:57
msgid "Close Relay 0: 01 05 00 00 00 00 CD CA"
msgstr "Zapnout relé 0: 01 05 00 00 00 00 CD CA"

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:58
msgid "Open Relay 1: 01 05 00 01 FF 00 DD FA"
msgstr "Vypnout relé 1: 01 05 00 01 FF 00 DD FA"

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:59
msgid "Close Relay 1: 01 05 00 01 00 00 9C 0A"
msgstr "Zapnout relé 1: 01 05 00 01 00 00 9C 0A"

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:60
msgid "Open Relay 2: 01 05 00 02 FF 00 2D FA"
msgstr "Vypnout relé 2: 01 05 00 02 FF 00 2D FA"

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:61
msgid "Close Relay 2: 01 05 00 02 00 00 6C 0A"
msgstr "Zapnout relé 2: 01 05 00 02 00 00 6C 0A"

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:62
msgid "Open Relay 3: 01 05 00 03 FF 00 7C 3A"
msgstr "Vypnout relé 3: 01 05 00 03 FF 00 7C 3A"

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:63
msgid "Close Relay 3: 01 05 00 03 00 00 3D CA"
msgstr "Zapnout relé 3: 01 05 00 03 00 00 3D CA"

#: plugins/modbus_stations/templates/modbus_stations_help.html:64
msgid "Flip Relay 0: 01 05 00 00 55 00 F2 9A"
msgstr "Invertovat stav relé 0: 01 05 00 00 55 00 F2 9A"

