#: plugins/shelly_cloud_integrator/templates/shelly_cloud_integration_help.html:8
msgid ""
"This extension adds integration of Shelly devices into the OSPy ecosystem. "
"After setting up this extension and adding devices, these devices will "
"appear in OSPy sensors and you will be able to work with them further."
